00:04:47.600 --> 00:04:48.770
Everyone!

110
00:04:48.770 --> 00:04:51.730
Gather 'round! Gather 'round!

111
00:04:51.730 --> 00:04:55.690
Here's a sheet of paper—
no gimmicks or setup!

112
00:04:55.690 --> 00:04:58.070
One sheet becomes two!

113
00:04:58.070 --> 00:05:01.860
Two sheets become four!
Four sheets become eight!

114
00:05:01.860 --> 00:05:07.250
Eight to sixteen, then thirty-two to sixty-four!

115
00:05:09.790 --> 00:05:12.380
I give you the fluttering dance of...

116
00:05:12.380 --> 00:05:19.630
a springtime sakura shower
and the snowfall of Wano's early evening!

117
00:05:28.680 --> 00:05:33.560
Now you've witnessed how
truly sharp this named blade is!

118
00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:35.690
A simple graze from it...

119
00:05:36.320 --> 00:05:39.030
See how easily it can cut you!

120
00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:48.370
But, watch this!

121
00:05:49.250 --> 00:05:52.210
What I have here is toad oil!

122
00:05:52.670 --> 00:05:56.340
If you apply it to a wound...!

123
00:05:59.130 --> 00:06:01.170
Ta-dah!

124
00:06:01.510 --> 00:06:04.090
Look! You see?!

125
00:06:04.090 --> 00:06:06.720
This is how it works!

126
00:06:06.720 --> 00:06:08.760
The bleeding's stopped, too!

127
00:06:09.390 --> 00:06:11.850
This toad oil is an East Blue specialty!

128
00:06:11.850 --> 00:06:13.940
Come and get some!

129
00:06:13.940 --> 00:06:15.730
– I'll have some!
– Me too!

130
00:06:15.730 --> 00:06:18.190
You folks have a good eye!

131
00:06:18.190 --> 00:06:22.070
Now, gather 'round! Gather 'round!

132
00:06:22.030 --> 00:06:22.070
Usohachi



